  "description": "<p>Feeling 'shag' but also stagnant?  Why not do the same but seek development, exposure, and a livelier team culture?</p><p>We’re looking for driven peeps to level up with us in sales, marketing, and business development.</p><p><strong>Why should I?</strong></p><p>• ✈️ Overseas opportunities on us</p><p>• 📝 One-on-one coaching</p><p>• 🛗Spirited and collaborative team</p><p>• ❤️‍🔥 Supportive, close-knit culture</p><p>• 📈 Advancement for impact, not just SOP box-checking<br /></p><p><strong>What do I do?</strong></p><p>• Carry out marketing campaigns and team-building</p><p>• Build rapport with clients</p><p>• Have fun and connect with colleagues<br /></p><p><strong>What I need to have?</strong></p><p>• Positive mindset </p><p>• Constant learner</p><p>• Be yourself</p><p>If these 'womp womp' moments have been around for too long, take that step with us and do it for the plot.✨️✨️✨️</p><p>Apply now!</p>",
